<template><AdminTablePage title="论坛管理" desc="审核帖子、删除违规内容，维护求职社区秩序" :list="list" :total="total" :loading="loading" :query="query" :show-add="false" @load="load" :action-width="220"><template #toolbar><el-input v-model="query.title" placeholder="帖子标题" clearable style="width:220px"/><el-select v-model="query.auditStatus" clearable placeholder="审核状态" style="width:130px"><el-option label="待审核" :value="0"/><el-option label="通过" :value="1"/><el-option label="驳回" :value="2"/></el-select><el-button type="primary" @click="reload">查询</el-button></template><template #columns><el-table-column prop="title" label="标题" min-width="220"/><el-table-column prop="authorName" label="作者" width="100"/><el-table-column prop="category" label="版块" width="110"/><el-table-column label="数据" width="180"><template #default="{row}">浏览{{row.viewCount}}/赞{{row.likeCount}}/评{{row.commentCount}}</template></el-table-column><el-table-column label="审核" width="90"><template #default="{row}"><el-tag :type="row.auditStatus===1?'success':row.auditStatus===2?'danger':'warning'">{{['待审核','通过','驳回'][row.auditStatus]}}</el-tag></template></el-table-column></template><template #rowActions="{row}"><el-button text type="success" @click="audit(row,1)">通过</el-button><el-button text type="danger" @click="audit(row,2)">驳回</el-button><el-button text type="danger" @click="del(row)">删除</el-button></template></AdminTablePage></template><script setup>import{reactive,ref,onMounted}from'vue';import{ElMessageBox}from'element-plus';import AdminTablePage from '@/components/AdminTablePage.vue';import{adminApi}from'@/api';const query=reactive({pageNum:1,pageSize:10,title:'',auditStatus:''});const list=ref([]),total=ref(0),loading=ref(false);const load=async()=>{loading.value=true;try{const p={...query};if(p.auditStatus==='')delete p.auditStatus;const r=await adminApi.forumPosts(p);list.value=r.data.records;total.value=Number(r.data.total)}finally{loading.value=false}};const reload=()=>{query.pageNum=1;load()};const audit=async(row,s)=>{await adminApi.auditPost(row.id,s);load()};const del=row=>ElMessageBox.confirm('确定删除该帖子？').then(async()=>{await adminApi.delPost(row.id);load()});onMounted(load)</script>